
Blue Machine Commands

*******************************************************************************

sudo ip netns add blue

sudo ip link set veth1 netns blue

sudo ip netns exec blue ip link list

sudo ip netns exec blue ip addr add 172.168.1.10/24 dev veth1

sudo ip netns exec blue ip link set dev veth1 up





To Login to BLue machine

*******************************************************************************

sudo ip netns exec blue /bin/bash

